ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇人來CHECK  咁多萬人入境邊有可能遂個CHECK</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係理由"},{"pid":"82b03dd10dbeaf3b40ec4c6fde4ecfcc8e75cc1e","tid":273952,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇樣check<br />\n<br />\n好似一般連登仔應該無咩要check既機會</blockquote><br />\n咁即係如果連登仔運毒都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣唔起眼"},{"pid":"27f7b3196ca5532a701850677c9eb7014401a620","tid":273952,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇人來CHECK  咁多萬人入境邊有可能遂個CHECK</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係理由</blockquote><br />\ncheck左你唔知啫，你行李一落機，用緝毒犬聞咪仲快。"},{"pid":"877d045c60186d3ec681d8068edfe0385a3ad3fa","tid":273952,"uid":67116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇人來CHECK  咁多萬人入境邊有可能遂個CHECK</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係理由</blockquote><br />\ncheck左你唔知啫，你行李一落機，用緝毒犬聞咪仲快。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係諗唔到<br />\n再出海關捉9你"},{"pid":"a2d12df2d8ac27f3c803fa0c5a57f3ecd6064d72","tid":273952,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇人來CHECK  咁多萬人入境邊有可能遂個CHECK</blockquote><br />\n依個唔係理由</blockquote><br />\ncheck左你唔知啫，你行李一落機，用緝毒犬聞咪仲快。</blockquote><br />\n的確係，行李未上海關大堂之前，下面已經有成隊海關加幾隻狗加x光機係到check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad16c669c4e62d99982176b976201d12136187e","tid":273952,"uid":19505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"試下最清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d845bf489e6b453003b20a95b29114df9c9015","tid":273952,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:59:38.000Z","msg"